{"tid":300632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓阿豬媽坐廉航香港快運除鞋晾腳   逼港女調位","createTime":"2017-06-28T05:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T05:39:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54179e7422d4d918699a0244b1e33d467d43159a","tid":300632,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498613856_5200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170628%2Flarge%2F1498613856_5200.jpg&h=68e3b395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛機座椅晾腳並不是支那客「專利」，有香港女網民近日在facebook貼文，指來自南韓的一名「阿豬媽」在廉航香港快運（HK Express）突然拍醒，並以流利但沒有禮貌的英語叫網民調位，因為想「坐得更舒服」。<br />\n<br />\n女網民表示自己並沒有拉低椅背，應該沒有影響她，所以就沒有理會。然而南韓「阿豬媽」就跟同行2人再次拍醒她，她要求對方找空姐處理。空姐之後十分為難地向她說，原來「阿豬媽」想除鞋伸直雙腳，但乘客可以選擇不理會，但可能會有臭味。網民聽到當然要調位，而「阿豬媽」得償所願雙腳直接「晾」到前座椅背上，還向對調了位的網民怒目而視。<br />\n<br />\n網友紛紛留言寫道：「不知所謂！」「太過份，是否有病？」「泡菜粉絲點睇呀？支那同韓國真係孖生姊妹國嚟，野蠻行為一樣樣。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498611698_f665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170628%2Flarge%2F1498611698_f665.jpg&h=016e7faf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498611699_9818.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170628%2Flarge%2F1498611699_9818.jpg&h=d613c763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498613886_5ad7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170628%2Flarge%2F1498613886_5ad7.jpg&h=a841e7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498614259_1789.jpg\" data-thumbnail